Package jackstockley.addressbookcli

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressBook
    This program allows a user to interact with an address book that is saved on a MySQL database over the Internet!
    AddressHelper
    This part of the program helps connect the user to the MySQL database and address table by formating data and allowing user input
    AppTest
    Unit test for simple App.
    ConnectionHelper
    This part of the program help with getting and saving connection to a CSV file and also helps with duplicate checking and password salting and hashing
    FrontendHelper
    This part of the program helps with random tasks to make the program function Part of the functions are logging and allowing for any data or time searching on the database
    OccupationHelper
    This part of the program helps connect the user to the MySQL database and occupation table by formatting data and allowing user input
    PersonHelper
    This part of the program helps connect the user to the MySQL database and the person table by formatting data and allowing user input
    Updater
    This small part of the program helps check for version updated of the program and tells the user how to download them
